---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets'
import frankstallone from '@assets/2023-Frank-Stallone-Web-Marketing-Expert.png'
---

<div class="region region-space-3xl-4xl bg-gray-1400 text-gray-800 pb-zero">
  <div class="switcher">
    <div class="box flow bg-transparent text-gray-800">
      <p class="text-step-1">
        I'm a husband, father, <span
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-vivid-400 to-indigo-vivid-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >
          designer</span
        >, <code class="bg-gray-1300 text-blue-vivid-500">developer</code>, and <span
          class="text-gold-500"
          style="filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(222, 198, 154, 0.5));"
          >hopeless optimist</span
        >.
      </p>
      <p class="text-step-0 text-gray-900">
        Throughout my career, I've bridged the gap between design and
        development, as well as between marketing and SaaS products, to produce
        stellar user experiences. I enjoy mentoring and have worked in lab
        environments at small and large organizations.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center relative overflow-hidden flex items-end">
      <Picture
        src={frankstallone}
        widths={[300, 800, 2000, frankstallone.width]}
        sizes={`(max-width: 300px) 300px, (max-width: 800px) 800px, (max-width: 1600px) 2000px, ${frankstallone.width}px`}
        class="object-contain h-auto"
        alt="The Internet's favorite Frank Stallone"
        formats={['avif', 'webp']}
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
